          "tarea": "$\\sqrt{x-7} + 2 = \\sqrt{x+9}$"
        },
        {
          "letra": "b",
          "puntos": 1.25,
          "tarea": "$|2x - 4| = x - 2$"
        },
        {
          "letra": "c",
          "puntos": 1.25,
          "tarea": "$\\log_{3}(x+1) + \\log_{3}(x-5) = 3$"
        },
        {
          "letra": "d",
          "puntos": 1.25,
          "tarea": "$2^{x+1} \\cdot 2^{2x-3} \\cdot 2^{x+4} = 16$"
        },
        {
          "letra": "e",
          "puntos": 1.25,
          "tarea": "$25^{x} - 6 \\cdot 5^{x+1} + 125 = 0$"
        },
        {
          "letra": "f",
          "puntos": 1.25,
          "tarea": "Sistema: $\\begin{cases} 3^{x} \\cdot 3^{y+1} = 9 \\\\ \\sqrt{x+1} = y + 10 \\end{cases}$"
        },
        {
          "letra": "g",
          "puntos": 1.25,
          "tarea": "Sistema: $\\begin{cases} \\log(x \\cdot y^{2}) = 5 \\\\ 2\\log(x) - \\log(y^{3}) = 3 \\end{cases}$"
        },
        {
          "letra": "h",
          "puntos": 1.25,
          "tarea": "Inequació: $\\dfrac{3x-1}{2} \\geq x - \\dfrac{x+3}{3}$"
        }
